furniture.name: Coombes
furniture.description: Benchmade with certified sustainable engineered hardwood that's kiln-dried to prevent warping. Synthetic webbing suspension.

furniture.name: Keeve Set
furniture.description: It’s casual, it’s coastal, it’s unexpected...With its good looks and excellent craftsmanship, it's a perfect bed side table to store valuables. The rattan frame – steamed and bent into shape by hand – is accented with hand-wrapped rattan peel around the joints giving a antique look to it.

furniture.name: Nille
furniture.description: It’s casual, it’s coastal, it’s unexpected...With its good looks and excellent craftsmanship, this is everything we love in a chair. The rattan frame – steamed and bent into shape by hand – is accented with hand-wrapped rattan peel around the joints and can be used with or without a cushion. A low-seat profile completes the relaxed vibe.

furniture.name: Momo
furniture.description: An accordion screen is a standout for so many reasons. It can define different areas in your home (a boon for open floor plans), create an intimate corner, and add a striking design element to the room. Here, three caned panels are edged in hand-wrapped in rattan to achieve gorgeous texture and tone. Brass end caps on the feet add an elevating finishing touch.

furniture.name: Penemille
furniture.description: Tight back seat is high-resilience topped with an extra layer of comfort. Self-welt detailing. Made in North Carolina, USA of domestic and imported materials.

furniture.name: Kappu
furniture.description: Reese has all the thoughtful details of a well-designed piece. We started with a sturdy oak frame and gave it extra character with Asian-inspired legs and a cerused finish. Next, we added a roomy storage drawer and a pull-out shelf that can serve as a mini bar when guests arrive. Your very own curation would make this all the more special – your favorite books, your favorite mementos.
